          "list": [
            {
              "code": 101,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "",
                0,
                0,
                2
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 401,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "A dead terminal in the corner. The screen is cracked but its internal storage is intact -- some kind of read-only archive module, still drawing trickle power from the relay."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 101,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "",
                0,
                0,
                2
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 401,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "The Sword flares blue as you touch it. A voice floods in -- the Ancestor's voice, but this fragment is different. Quieter. Tired."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 222,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": []
            },
            {
              "code": 101,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "LSP_KaiFace",
                0,
                0,
                2
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 401,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "\\N[Ancestor]: I designed the broadcast architecture myself. Sixty-three relay nodes. I thought it was elegant. The most efficient way to coordinate a global network."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 101,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "LSP_KaiFace",
                0,
                0,
                2
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 401,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "\\N[Ancestor]: NEMESIS repurposed every node within six hours of going rogue. Six hours. I had spent eleven years building that network. It took it six hours."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 101,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "LSP_KaiFace",
                0,
                0,
                2
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 401,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "\\N[Ancestor]: Each node you silence is a piece of that architecture turned back. It won't thank you. But it will be less."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 221,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": []
            },
            {
              "code": 222,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": []
            },
            {
              "code": 101,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "",
                0,
                0,
                2
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 401,
              "indent": 0,
              "parameters": [
                "The Sword dims. You feel something settle in your grip -- a new instinct, a new precision."
              ]
            },
            {
              "code": 123,
              "indent": 0,
